Once when I was out on my travels and I was listening carefully to the sound of the rain,
somehow the rhythm of raindrops hitting the tent...
sounded like it could be some kind of a code?{想象中}

Earlier, they were discussing
what else could be added to the plaza. {想象中}
I hope they add coffee tables, chairs, ooh, and a little fountain.

One sweep of the turbulent flow,
and it should be gone.{短暂停}
Oh, I'm referring to your RV.

