The Camp is quite exposed to the winds,
One can see what's happening here from quite far away...{短暂停}
Oh, not that I've seen anything in particular.

But what about those creatures,
Won't the light keep them from sleeping at night? {打哈欠}
Or perhaps... does the companion grass have some sort of soporific effect?
